HEADWORD: normalcy
<hw>nor"mal*cy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality, state,
or fact of being normal; the normal situation or condition; <as>as, the
point of <ex>normalcy</ex></as>.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> normality.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

